Center of Lake
At long last, your punting has brought you so far out that the Lake Shore is now shrouded in fog, whereas here the mists have parted like a curtain, admitting a thin ray of twilight that reveals a punting raft much like the one you're in, only this one is charred to cinders.  It floats in and out of the mist, then settles right before you. Gradually you discern a blackened skeleton pinned by a trenchant blade stuck fast in the wood.  The golden pommel gleams brightly, creating an eerie metallic rainbow against the receding mists.

> take mindsword

> take mindsword
With your stout limbs, you wrench the Mindsword free from the fire-hardened timbers.
You now bear the Sword of Mind.
Your score went up by 25!
Where the blade was sunk, you see an iron collar with a'V' shackled to the skeletal remains of the Brethren's last victim.  The burnt raft then drifts into the fog.
