Ruffians Clearing
Scorched trees and blasted clumps of heath surround you here on the edges of a moor to the north and west.  The trail through this clearing is littered with broken bits of iron and leaves besotted with blood.  You feel malevolent eyes following your moves through here.
You can go south, northwest, north or east.
You can see Ruff Ian and Rap Scallion.

