Radiant with forbidden power, the Crystal summons the Dark Sword.  Attuned to its proddings, the black blade spins through the air, beyond your control, to the waiting paw of the wizard.  In a metallic whisper, he gloats, "Our Master of Ceremonies will be pleased by this offering."
The wizard's diabolical chanting continues as the ground shudders, and in the floor, the outlines of the Crypt glow eerily as the Casket within begins to quake.
