In a burst of swashbuckling fervor, Voltan crosses swords with staccato taps and startling twists that sends the Mindsword across the chapel, where it bangs into the Conclave's hymnals and drops into a hex on the floor. Its charms burn the Mindstone bright as the sun, whereat the Elfin fist looses its hold. As the Black Wizard scurries over, you catch sight of Voltan holding Rap over the Crypt as she fights for dear life.
> save rap

> save rap
You rush headlong at Voltan from the side, knocking Rap clear from the Crypt, but plowing straight into your revolting brother.  As you collide, he lets go his weapon and swings you in an icy grip. For a second you are only inches from his worm-eaten face, nearly gagging at the stench, but he swerves you past his metal helmet and billowed cape. Stumbling back two steps, you careen from the dais and flop with outstretched arms into the enormous bloody Cauldron!At first, all is dark, all silent. Then a quake, a thunderous report, and excruciating pain. As if all your limbs were torn off. Then a whoosh and crack as if the bottom fell out of the earth. You seem to be floating toward a dim light. There is a familiar form beckoning you from that distant star. She herself is the light, robed in it, a White Queen. Music floods your senses, the songs you always wanted to hear, and new ones yet to be recorded. She extends her hand, and you take it.There are indeed many worlds. You have played a part in saving this one.
Thou hast scored 60 out of 360.
